    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if there is no way forward? like what if the \"pause\" just makes it more obvious that there's nothing left to go back to? it feels like some people are just meant to keep struggling until they finally just... stop. like it's a more logical end than just dragging it out forever.",
